{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 204441, "create_time": 1654927104, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "按照我的理解（不一定对），导师自己是不能拿的，应该都给学生（和其他真正干活的人）但不排除有的导师发给学生然后让学生转给自己", "timestamp": 1654927104}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 204450, "create_time": 1654927516, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "劳务费只能发给别人，导师自己不能拿", "timestamp": 1654927516}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 204459, "create_time": 1654927768, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "谢谢Bob补充，确实要看类目。我是了解是项目负责人自己不能拿劳务费。一个典型的项目预算除了劳务费之外，还有其他类目，我就不太了解了。设备费、材料费、测试化验加工费、差旅费、会议费、国际合作与交流费、出版/文献/信息传播/知识产权事务费，劳务费，专家咨询费，其他。", "timestamp": 1654927768}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 204466, "create_time": 1654927919, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "谢谢alice和bob，dz还有个疑问，如果导师不能拿很多的话，一直做横向的目的是什么，拿到的项目经费达到学校考核指标不就可以躺平了吗", "timestamp": 1654927919}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 204490, "create_time": 1654928192, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "肯定可以拿吧，某种合法的方式，导师自己也算出力了", "timestamp": 1654928192}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 204717, "create_time": 1654933073, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "纵向项目的会议、差旅可以覆盖导师自己的出差、吃饭等开销。导师可以给自己开绩效工资。", "timestamp": 1654933073}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 204723, "create_time": 1654933171, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "横向和企业的合作越多，开的绩效工作就能越高。", "timestamp": 1654933171}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 204732, "create_time": 1654933261, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "设备和材料的采购回扣就不细说了。\n", "timestamp": 1654933261}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 204911, "create_time": 1654935727, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "这样子拉项目就说得通了，那么导师虚报项目人数是一种普遍存在或者合法的现象吗", "timestamp": 1654935727}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 204951, "create_time": 1654936515, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "横向感觉很能赚钱啊 老师特别喜欢做横向 越接越多 虽然不知道怎么实现的\n", "timestamp": 1654936515}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 205292, "create_time": 1654942460, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Eve: 反正我知道的几个实验室都有虚报参与的人数和工作时长。合法不合法嘛，至少是灰色地带了。", "timestamp": 1654942460}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 205407, "create_time": 1654944193, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 老师给自己开绩效是拿劳务费之外的部分，虚报人数拿劳务费？", "timestamp": 1654944193}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 205458, "create_time": 1654945347, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 虚报人数是因为有预算或者合同金额，凑人数出来。企业横向课题管理比较宽松，大致可以认为除了学校和系的管理费之外，剩下的都是老师（因为审批签字都是自己签字）。可以参见知乎问题：https://www.zhihu.com/question/508370600。", "timestamp": 1654945347}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 205460, "create_time": 1654945447, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "还有这个文章：https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/19572795", "timestamp": 1654945447}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 205530, "create_time": 1654946512, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Dave: 谢谢Dave，看了之后感觉老师能拿挺多的，横向比纵向宽松，报销范围广，大概还能拿20%的现金，具体要看签订的合同了", "timestamp": 1654946512}], "create_time": 1654926963, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1654936515, "likenum": 9, "n_attentions": 9, "n_comments": 10, "pid": 62953, "poll": null, "reply": 10, "text": "有点好奇理工科的项目经费都是怎么分配的，包括横向和纵向，导师能拿多少，导师和学生是共用一个池子吗，是不是发给学生导师自己拿的就少了，求科普", "timestamp": 1654926963}}